BBK01.WT5011: Exchange rates on the Frankfurt exchange /ffrs 100 = DM .../ up to December 1959 / France

General: Spot middle rates in Deutsche Mark; difference between buying or selling rate and middle rate D-Mark 0.0010. From 4 May 1953 to 31 December 1959 official quotation on the Frankfurt exchange. Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 1960: ffrs 100 = NF 1 (french New Franc). Rates from 1960, see wt5012.
